<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Verified</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .highlight {
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .next-steps {
      background-color: #dbeafe;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>✓ Email Verified!</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>

    <p>Thank you for verifying your email address!</p>

    <div class="highlight">
      <p style="font-size: 48px; margin: 10px 0;">✓</p>
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Your email has been successfully verified</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="next-steps">
      <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Your account is now awaiting administrator approval</li>
        <li>We will review your details (usually within 24 hours)</li>
        <li>You will receive an email confirming approval</li>
        <li>Then you can fully use all features</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <p>In the meantime, you can explore the platform and get ready.</p>

    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View Dashboard</a>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      Thank you for your patience!<br>
      <strong>The Boilerplate Team</strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent automatically. Please do not reply to it.</p>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Boilerplate. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
